OL,3,CQuestion Time: Policing minister Chris
OL,4,CPhilp appears to confuse Congo and
OL,5,CRwanda
OL,7,FPolicing minister Chris Philp appeared
OL,8,Fto confuse the countries of Rwanda and
OL,9,Fthe Democratic Republic of the Congo
OL,10,Fon Question Time.
OL,12,FResponding to an audience member's
OL,13,Fquestion during the BBC One programme,
OL,14,Fthe MP for Croydon South seemed to ask
OL,15,Fwhether "Rwanda is a different country
OL,16,Fto Congo".
