OL,3,CQuestion Time: Policing minister Chris
OL,4,CPhilp appears to confuse Congo and
OL,5,CRwanda
OL,7,FThe audience member, who said he came
OL,8,Ffrom the Democratic Republic of the
OL,9,FCongo, asked: "Had my family members
OL,10,Fcome from Goma (a city on the
OL,11,Fcountry's border) on a crossing right
OL,12,Fnow, would they then be sent back to
OL,13,Fthe country they are supposedly
OL,14,Fwarring ` Rwanda?
OL,16,F"Does that make any sense to you?"
OL,18,FMr Philp replied: "No, I think there's
OL,19,Fan exclusion on people from Rwanda
OL,20,Fbeing sent to Rwanda."
