OL,5,CRwanda
OL,7,FAfter the audience member objected
OL,8,Fthat his parents were "not from
OL,9,FRwanda", the Conservative MP appeared
OL,10,Fto ask: "Well, I mean, Rwanda is a
OL,11,Fdifferent country to Congo isn't it?
OL,13,F"It's a different country?"
OL,15,FThe comment caused a short outburst of
OL,16,Flaughter from some members of the
OL,17,Fdebate programme's audience as shadow
OL,18,Fhealth secretary Wes Streeting's eyes
OL,19,Fdarted around the room.
