OL,7,FMr Philp continued: "There is a clause
OL,8,Fin the legislation that says if
OL,9,Fsomebody would suffer, I think the
OL,10,Fphrase is 'serious and irreversible
OL,11,Fharm' by being sent somewhere, they
OL,12,Fwouldn't be sent.
OL,14,F"So there is that safety mechanism
OL,15,Fbuilt into the legislation."
OL,17,FThere has been a long history of
OL,18,Fviolent conflict between the
OL,19,Fneighbouring African countries.
